text: Félicien Lekim (25 April 1883 - 20 June 1916) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's artistic individual all-around event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1883 births Category:1916 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:People from Hautmont
